[Name] NCMPC++
[Summary] An ncurses mpd client inspired by ncmpc
[Description] Ncmpcpp has UI very similar to ncmpc's one, but it provides new useful features such as support for regular expressions in search engine, extended song format, items filtering, last.fm support, ability to sort playlist, local filesystem browser and other minor functions.
[License] GPL v2.0
[Homepage] http://unkart.ovh.org/ncmpcpp
